element_text:
Sambeskatningsbidrag mellem de sambeskattede
selskaber, som ikke er afregnet på balancedagen,
klassificeres som sambeskatningsbidrag under enten
tilgodehavender eller gældsforpligtelser.
Joint tax contributions between the jointly taxed
companies which have not been settled at the balance
sheet date are classified as joint tax contributions in
receivables or liabilities.
